From: Rai Harninder-B01044 <harninder.rai@freescale.com>
Date: Wed, 28 Oct 2015 12:51:50 +0530
Subject: [PATCH 0060/1383] arm64: Move LS2080A compilation under
 ARCH_LAYERSCAPE

ARCH_LAYERSCAPE is the common define for Layerscape SoC family
So, move the compilation of LS2085A device tree files under
this define

Signed-off-by: Rai Harninder-B01044 <harninder.rai@freescale.com>
[Original patch taken from QorIQ-SDK-V2.0-20160527-yocto]
Signed-off-by: Yanjiang Jin <yanjiang.jin@windriver.com>
---
 arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile | 2 +-
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile
index f80315e..3a0d206 100644
--- a/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile
+++ b/arch/arm64/boot/dts/freescale/Makefile
@@ -1,4 +1,4 @@
-dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_FSL_LS2085A) += fsl-ls2085a-simu.dtb fsl-ls2085a-qds.dtb fsl-ls2085a-rdb.dtb
+dtb-$(CONFIG_ARCH_LAYERSCAPE) += fsl-ls2085a-simu.dtb fsl-ls2085a-qds.dtb fsl-ls2085a-rdb.dtb
  
 always		:= $(dtb-y)
 subdir-y	:= $(dts-dirs)
